}}|| Brenda Box<br>{{flag|Texas}}|| Susanne Pottenger<br>{{flag|Arizona}}|| Nancy Rich<br>{{flag|Missouri}}|| Patricia Barnstable<br>{{flag|Kentucky}}\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| [[Miss USA 1972|1972]] || [[Tanya Wilson]]<br>{{flag|Hawaii}}|| Alberta Philips<br>{{flag|New York (state)|name=New York}}|| Kim Christina Hobson<br>{{flag|California}}|| Coni Ensor<br>{{flag|Florida|1900}}|| Kathleen Ann Kehlmier<br>{{flag|Ohio}}\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| [[Miss USA 1973|1973]] || [[Amanda Jones (Miss USA)|Amanda Jones]]<br>{{flag|Illinois}}|| [[Susan Carlson]]<br>{{flag|New York (state)|name=New York}}|| Gayle White<br>{{flag|Rhode Island}}|| Sherry Nix<br>{{flag|Arizona}}||[[Betty Jo Grove]]<br>{{flag|Maryland}}\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| [[Miss USA 1974|1974]] || [[Karen Morrison]]<br>{{flag|Illinois}}|| Barbara Cooper<br>{{flag|New York (state)|name=New York}}|| Mary Cook<br>{{flag|Wisconsin}}|| Gayle Gorrell<br>{{flag|California}}|| Marcia Burton<br>{{flag|North Carolina|1885}}\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| [[Miss USA 1975|1975]] || [[Summer Bartholomew]]<br>{{flag|California}}|| Pamela Flowers<br>{{flag|Alabama}}|| Constance Dorn<br>{{flag|North Carolina|1885}}||[[Mary Humes]]<br>{{flag|Florida|1900}} || Aundie Evers<br>{{flag|Texas}}\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| [[Miss USA 1976|1976]] || [[Barbara Peterson]]<br>{{flag|Minnesota|1957}}|| Kevin Gale<br>{{flag|Michigan}}|| Gail Atchison<br>{{flag|Oregon}}|| Virginia Murray<br>{{flag|South Carolina}}|| Robyn Sanders<br>{{flag|Louisiana|1912}}\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| [[Miss USA 1977|1977]] || [[Kimberly Tomes]]<br>{{flag|Texas}}|| Mary O'Neal Contino<br>{{flag|Nevada|1929}}|| Deborah Cossette<br>{{flag|Minnesota|1957}}|| Pamela Gergely<br>{{flag|California}}||[[Lynn Herring ]]<br>{{flag|Virginia}}\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| [[Miss USA 1978|1978]] || [[Judi Andersen]]<br>{{flag|Hawaii}}|| Diane Pollard<br>{{flag|Massachusetts}}|| Barbra Horan<br>{{flag|Texas}}||