 Baldwin (Coronation Street)]]\n** [[Viv Baldwin]]\n** [[Warren Baldwin]]\n*In the soap opera ''[[The Young and the Restless]]'':\n** [[Eden Baldwin]]\n** [[Lauren Fenmore Baldwin]]\n** [[Michael Baldwin]]\n** [[River Baldwin]]\n\n== See also ==\n* {{look from|Baldwin}}\n* {{look from|Balduin}}\n* {{look from|Baudouin}}\n* {{look from|Boudewijn}}\n* [[Baldwin I (disambiguation)]]\n* [[Baldwin II (disambiguation)]]\n* [[Baldwin III (disambiguation)]]\n* [[Baldwin IV]]\n* [[Baldwin V]]\n* [[Baldwin VI (disambiguation)]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{given name|type=both}}\n\n[[Category:Germanic-language surnames]]\n", "name_user": "Barkeep49", "label": "safe", "comment": "Removing link(s):Wikipedia:Articles for deletion/Judy Baldwinclosed as soft delete (XFDcloser)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Baldwin_(name)"}
